snippet.title: Arabians Doubt[アラビアンズ・ダウト～The engagement on desert～] PSP OP
snippet.description:
I really don't know if a should keep doing this. Well... i'm gonna think about it.... YEAH I SHOULD!

Set after the normal route in Arabian’s Lost where you win the bet but don’t get a husband. Eileen finds herself forced to act as ruler after her parents take off one day on a trip.

Production: QuinRose
Release Date: 2014/01/30
Artist: Naozumi Takahashi
Song: Doubt

Official site: http://quinrose.com/game/arabian_doubt/top.html
To download: http://vndb.org/v11132

Other sites:
http://eroyume.com/
http://fuwanovel.org/
